OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLeena Manimekalai: India   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdirector criticised for    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fposter of movie 'Kaali'    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A film poster that depicts a woman     
OL,6, dressed as Hindu goddess Kali smoking a
OL,7, cigarette has sparked anger in India.  
OL,9,FDirector Leena Manimekalai tweeted the 
OL,10,Fposter of her new film Kaali -         
OL,11,Fdescribed as a "performance            
OL,12,Fdocumentary" - on Saturday.            
OL,14,FSince then, it has generated hundreds  
OL,15,Fof responses from angry Hindus, who    
OL,16,Fhave accused her of offending their    
OL,17,Freligious sentiments.                  
OL,19,FKali, the Hindu goddess of destruction,
OL,20,Fis worshipped by millions of people.   
